column2: ggplot(data, aes(x = platelets)) + geom_histogram(binwidth = 25000, colour =  "white", fill = "red", alpha = 0.7) + labs(title = "Histogram of Platelet Count") + geom_density(eval(bquote(aes(y=..count.. *25000))),colour="black") + geom_vline(xintercept = 150000, linetype = "dashed") + geom_vline(xintercept = 450000, linetype = "dashed")
